InsiderType.description:
The insider type information is used to provide info to Regulation 0.  The Regulation 0 is a Federal Reserve regulation that places limits and stipulations on the credit extensions a member bank can offer to its executive officers, principal shareholders, and directors. Possible values: 
   Director, Employee, Officer, PrincipalShareholder, Shareholder, Executive, ServiceCorporationEmployee, Child, Spouse, Parent, Relative, AffiliateFinancialInstitution, HoldingCompany, MainShareHolder, RelationshipInterest.
